{"tid":1136704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五一黃金周】中大合一亭淪遊客新景點 中國網推「打卡團」","createTime":"2019-05-03T07:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T17:07:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"729f94464e2524c0bb1d7a82000af9272a686715","tid":1136704,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190503/_2019050310521422324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190503%2F_2019050310521422324.jpg&h=897ce404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地一連四天的「五．一黃金周」，大批內地旅客來港旅行，除了山頂、金紫荊廣場等傳統著名景點外，近年有內地旅遊網站推出另類攻略，推介不少打卡「新景點」。其中，中文大學新亞書院的合一亭在黃金周期間更被「佔領」，不時有數十名自由行旅客排隊，等待在湖邊拍照，他們擺出不同姿勢，當中大部分人均操普通話。<br />\n<br />\n有內地遊客表示，從網上發現合一亭的照片，認為風景美麗，因此特意前來打卡；亦有遊客指，因為住在附近，瀏覽旅遊網站時發現該景點，因此順道前來拍照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190503/_2019050310521667918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190503%2F_2019050310521667918.jpg&h=e2717f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據內地的旅遊網站可見，除了推介傳統著名景點外，更推介網紅打卡地，當中包括樂華南邨、大館、理大，以及中大合一亭。該網站甚至以「隨手拍大片」為噱頭，推出打卡一日團，行程包括西環貨櫃碼頭、合一亭及彩虹邨等。<br />\n<br />\n因此遊客變多，中大學生會常務幹事陳偉霖昨日前往合一亭視察，指合一亭位於學生宿舍附近，由於現時正值考試季節，旅客到訪會影響學生溫書，希望校方能夠派人巡查。<br />\n<br />\n而中大回應傳媒表示，在五一黃金周假期期間會加強人手巡邏校園，如有遊人造成滋擾或收到投訴時，保安會即時作出勸喻，並提醒遊人必須遵守校園守則。而校方昨日並無收到有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190503/_2019050310521778141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190503%2F_2019050310521778141.jpg&h=71b5008d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1492393/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1492393%2F&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=1b7a502f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1492393%2F&h=82ed8733\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1492393/</a>"},{"pid":"060c159a278ae963b2fef5cfcbcf49993afee0de","tid":1136704,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"Yay !!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZD79Ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZD79Ot.jpg&h=03e77e94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fd342d1136f09cf659d5cd3f459422180272f75","tid":1136704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"屌我之前推啲香港秘景冇人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457f7d7d92d0743d8c17957d9d19e12c521d360d","tid":1136704,"uid":79410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"掛返啲佈景，天滅中共，香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b6be9cf49c2ce6e6d0b52cc8f21ff8da48a0fe","tid":1136704,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a385dd5abfe602a960a5033b2df27c4f9006dbf7","tid":1136704,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fd342d1136f09cf659d5cd3f459422180272f75","tid":1136704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"屌我之前推啲香港秘景冇人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"南區，清水灣，禮賓府嗰啲"},{"pid":"a911fc57863068d6c57cbdc0033fc85c6111f2f9","tid":1136704,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"五一黃金周就來到<br />\n今年嘅五一黃金周係「五大訴求，缺一不可，黃金經濟圈感謝周」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家花幾秒推、share 去 twitter/fb/ig，目的要重新定義五一，等五一黃金周變成支那禁字，防止港共開關放自由行<br />\n<br />\n[五一黃金週] 係時候包裝到同抗爭有關睇你支那夠唔夠膽放自由行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1960318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1960318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}